Class AbstractKeyValueTemplate

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jnosql.artemis.key.AbstractKeyValueTemplate
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    KeyValueTemplate

    public abstract class AbstractKeyValueTemplate
extends Object
implements KeyValueTemplate
    This class provides a skeletal implementation of the KeyValueTemplate interface, to minimize the effort required to implement this interface.
